lead_paragraph: Formula One championship leader Nico Rosberg is refusing to be rattled by reliability concerns as he prepares for his first 'match point' of the season in Mexico this weekend.

headline.print_headline: Rosberg Blocks Out Reliability Fears as 'Match Point' Looms
